# This file contains only npm-compatible settings. The pnpm-only supply-chain
# hardening (minimum-release-age etc.) lives in .pnpmrc so an `npm install`
# of this package does not print "Unknown config" warnings on every
# invocation. pnpm reads both files; npm reads only this one.
# Audit #36: previously these settings lived here as well and tripped npm's
# strict .npmrc reader.
